        <mxCell id="ep1" value="HelmRelease &amp;lt;claim&amp;gt;-epp  (chart v1.5.0)&#xa;   → InferencePool + EPP Deployment&#xa;CiliumNetworkPolicy  &amp;lt;claim&amp;gt;-epp&#xa;VMServiceScrape  &amp;lt;claim&amp;gt;-epp&#xa;&#xa;mutually exclusive with canaries[]" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=12;fontColor=#64748B;" vertex="1" parent="eppon">
